      "text": [
        "2584 - وَ فِي خَبَرٍ آخَرَ : «إِذَا نُودِيَ اَلْمُحْرِمُ فَلاَ يَقُلْ لَبَّيْكَ وَ لَكِنْ يَقُولُ يَا سَعْدُ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2584 - In another narration:\n\"If a Muhrim is called, he should not say 'Labbayk,' but rather say 'Ya Sa'd.'\""
        ]
      }
    }
  },
